a.n: King of Kings - Heroes Series, 31.10.2020 - Part I

p.d: One of the most recognizable brands in the world of kickboxing, King of Kings brings top fighters from around the globe and the most dedicated fans to the biggest arenas in the world to create an amazing spectacle. Incredible fights, powerful emotions, and high adrenaline is what every fighter and fan gets with the KOK Grand Prix Tournament Series.
